itemDescription: British MC, Singer and Actor originally from Nigeria

wikipedia_page.main: Aina Morenike Olukoga (born 12 May 1995) better known by her stage name Aina More is a British MC, singer and actor.

response: The exhibition was accompanied by an extensive programme of talks, events, performances and workshops, with participants including Lemi Ghariokwu, Kanya King, June Sarpong, Levi Roots, Yinka Ilori, Chibundu Onuzo, Aina More, Inua Ellams, Ade Solanke, Stephen Kelman, Jacob Sam-La Rose, and others."Event: West Africa: Word, Symbol, Song, at the British Library, 16 October 2015-16 February 2016", Africa In Words, 21 October 2015.
